content:
AccessCondition.IfNotChanged Method

Definition

Namespace:
Microsoft.Azure.Search.Models
Assembly:
Microsoft.Azure.Search.dll

In this Article

Constructs an access condition such that an operation will be performed only if the resource's current ETag value matches the specified resource's ETag value.

public static Microsoft.Azure.Search.Models.AccessCondition IfNotChanged (Microsoft.Azure.Search.Models.IResourceWithETag resource);
Parameters
resource
IResourceWithETag

A resource with an ETag value to check against the resource's ETag.

Returns
AccessCondition

An AccessCondition object that represents the If-Match condition.
